    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, neighbor! I\u2019m honestly a bit heartbroken to be letting this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for her to find a new home where she'll be just as pampered. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed, and kept in absolutely stunning condition. It truly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! She drives like a dream, and while there might be the tiniest, barely-there mark from a stray pebble, you\u2019d have to really squint to find it. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved with a capital L, come on by, let's have a chat, and I'll show you why this is the one!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
