      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level example for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection. This chassis exhibits zero structural fatigue, paired with a powertrain that delivers perfectly linear compression across the entire rev range. The valvetrain is whisper-quiet, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule and premium synthetic fluids. Every bushing has been inspected for optimal durometer, ensuring the suspension geometry remains surgical. Featuring a short-throw gearbox with zero lash and a cooling system optimized for maximum thermal efficiency, this vehicle performs with more vigor than the day it left the assembly line. Meticulously kept and stored in a climate-controlled environment, this is a turn-key investment for a driver who values peak engineering.",
      "price": 48900.0,
